                <li>Gymnasium and athletic facility floors</li>
                <li>Cafeteria and food service areas</li>
                <li>Library and media center applications</li>
                <li>Administrative and office space coatings</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="community-section">
              <h3>Business & Retail District</h3>
              <p>
