                <li>Professional office and service business coatings</li>
                <li>Healthcare and medical facility applications</li>
                <li>Automotive and service industry solutions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Process Excellence -->
      <section class="process-section">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Our Springboro Concrete Coating Process</h2>
          
          <div class="process-steps">
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">1</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Community-Focused Assessment</h3>
                <p>
                  Comprehensive evaluation of your Springboro property with understanding of community 
                  standards, family needs, and local architectural character.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">2</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Personalized Design</h3>
                <p>
                  Custom coating system development based on your specific requirements, lifestyle 
                  needs, and Springboro's community values and aesthetic preferences.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">3</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Professional Installation</h3>
                <p>
                  Expert application with attention to detail, respect for your property, and 
                  consideration for neighbors in Springboro's close-knit community environment.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-step">
              <div class="step-number">4</div>
              <div class="step-content">
                <h3>Satisfaction Guarantee</h3>
                <p>
                  Thorough quality inspection and customer satisfaction confirmation, ensuring your 
                  Springboro installation meets our high standards and your family's expectations.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Customer Testimonials -->
      <section class="testimonials">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Springboro Customer Experiences</h2>
          
          <div class="testimonials-grid">
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "With three kids in sports, our garage was constantly cluttered with equipment. 
                  The new epoxy floor makes organization easy and cleanup simple. Perfect solution 
                  for our active Springboro family."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>The Johnson Family</strong> - Springboro Residents
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Our community center needed flooring that could handle everything from basketball 
                  games to senior citizen activities. The results have been outstanding - durable, 
                  safe, and beautiful for all our community events."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Facility Manager</strong> - Springboro Community Center
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="testimonial">
              <div class="testimonial-content">
                <p>
                  "Our restaurant needed attractive, easy-to-clean floors that could handle high 
                  traffic while maintaining Springboro's welcoming atmosphere. Professional results 
                  that our customers notice and appreciate."
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <strong>Restaurant Owner</strong> - Downtown Springboro
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section id="contact" class="contact-section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="contact-content">
            <div class="contact-info">
              <h2>Enhance Your Springboro Property with Professional Concrete Coating</h2>
              <p>
                Ready to improve your Springboro property with expert concrete coating solutions? 
                Contact Queen City Surface Coatings for your personalized consultation and estimate.
              </p>
              
              <div class="contact-details">
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Phone:</strong> (513) 555-0123
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Email:</strong> info@queencitysurface.com
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Service Area:</strong> Springboro, OH and Warren County
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                  <strong>Business Hours:</strong> Monday-Saturday 7AM-7PM
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="service-promise">
                <h3>Our Springboro Service Commitment</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>Free consultations with family-focused recommendations</li>
                  <li>Community-sensitive installation practices</li>
                  <li>Licensed and insured throughout Ohio</li>
                  <li>Comprehensive warranty coverage</li>
                  <li>Warren County's trusted concrete coating specialists</li>
                  <li>Flexible scheduling for family and community needs</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="contact-form">
              <ContactForm />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    
    <Footer 
      footerLists={footerLists}
      footerSocials={footerSocials}
      copyrightName={settings.name}
    >
      <Logo slot="logo" />
    </Footer>
    
